data.description: Welcome to this captivating residence nestled in the heart of Gentry, Arkansas, featuring a delightful 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom layout with a thoughtfully designed split bedroom floor plan. As you step inside you'll be greeted by the warm and inviting ambiance of wood-inspired Luxury Vinyl Plank (LVP) flooring that graces the entirety of this home. Offering an expansive living space, the large living room seamlessly connects with the open kitchen creating an ideal setting for both family gatherings and entertaining guests. Adjacent to the kitchen a back deck awaits providing a perfect outdoor retreat just steps away from the heart of the home. 4 well appointed bedrooms offer ample storage and the split floor plan offers the ideal set up for individuals who value personal space. Situated in a great neighborhood adds an extra layer of appeal to this already attractive property. Act now and seize the chance to call 2005 Morgan Circle your home sweet home.
